name: Decotex 2 Piece Elegant Solid Sheer Window Curtain Panels Treatment Drapes (55" X 84", Purple)
shortDescription: Give your home decor style and sophistication when you decorate with sheer window panels. These beautiful rod pocket sheer curtains will bring a bright and cheerful look to any room. Each purchase is 2 panels. Each panel measures approximately 55 inches in width by 36, 45, 63, 84, 95, 108, or 120 inches in length so both panels together will be approximately 110 inches in width by 36, 45, 63, 84, 95, 108, or 120 inches in length.
